data.title: THE WALT DISNEY COMPANY
data.meta_description: Go.com is the top-level home on the Internet to the online properties of The Walt Disney Company.
data.text:
DISNEY PARKS

My Disney Experience - Walt Disney Resort

Discover the tools to plan & share your Disney World vacation.

Disneyland Resort

Imagination is the destination at Disneyland Resort in Anaheim, CA.

Disney Parks

Plan a family vacation to Disney Parks, cruises & other destinations.

Disney Cruise Line

Discover magical vacations with unique cruise activities for everyone.

Adventures by Disney

Planned & guided vacations with exciting itineraries all over the globe.

Aulani: A Disney Resort & Spa Disney

Hawaii Resort, a Hawaiian paradise with a touch of magic.

Disney Vacation Club

Disney Vacation Ownership and a flexible timeshare program.

Disneyland Star Wars

Season of the Force is a series of special events and experiences celebrating the Star Wars saga that takes place within Tomorrowland at Disneyland Park.

Toy Story Land

Shrink to the size of a toy in a new land at Disney's Hollywood Studios! Now open at Walt Disney World Resort.

DISNEY STORE

Disney Store: Disney's Official Online Store

Disney Store is the ultimate Disney shopping destination! Shop for costumes, clothes, toys, collectibles, décor, movies and more.

Disney Parks Merchandise

Bring home the magic with our must-haves merchandise inspired by Disney Parks.

Disney Princess Merchandise

Express yourself with toys, clothing, and more inspired by your favorite Disney Princesses at Disney Store.

Mickey Mouse Merchandise

Make magic with Mickey Mouse. Find an entire clubhouse of merchandise like toys, costumes, earhats, t-shirts, home decorations, party supplies and more at Disney Store.

Stitch Merchandise

Say aloha to Stitch merchandise from Disney's Lilo & Stitch for your entire ohana at Disney Store.

Toys for Kids

Make play time a blast with Disney toys. Find plush toys, Princess toys, action figures and much more at Disney Store.

Shop Disney Clothes: T-Shirts, Hoodies, PJs and More

Dress to impress with Disney clothes. Shop for hoodies, shirts, denim, activewear, pajamas and more at Disney Store.

ON DISNEY+

Dashing Through The Snow

Eddie Garrick and his daughter are taken on a magical adventure after meeting a mysterious man in a red suit named Nick, that just might restore his faith in Christmas.

Dancing with the Stars - Season 32

Watch full episodes from Season 32 of Dancing with the Stars, co-hosted by Alfonso Ribeiro and Julianne Hough. Live simulcast on ABC and Disney+. Also available the next day on Hulu.

Ahsoka

Former Jedi Knight Ahsoka Tano investigates an emerging threat to a vulnerable galaxy during the era of The New Republic. Streaming now on Disney+.

Loki - Season 2

The God of Mischief returns October 5 in season 2, which picks up in the aftermath of the shocking season 1 finale, when Loki finds himself in a battle for the soul of the Time Variance Authority.

Marvel Studios: Secret Invasion

Set in the present day MCU, Nick Fury learns of a clandestine invasion of Earth by a faction of shapeshifting Skrulls. New episodes streaming now on Disney+.

The Mandalorian

Set after the fall of the Empire and before the emergence of the First Order, we follow the travails of a lone gunfighter in the outer reaches of the galaxy. Streaming now on Disney+.

American Born Chinese

Based on the graphic novel by Gene Luen Yang. Follow the story of Jin Wang, an average teenager juggling his high school social life when he becomes unwittingly entailed in a battle of Chinese mythological gods.

Bluey

Binge the animated kids' hit, Bluey, a funny and honest look at modern family life through the eyes of an inexhaustible six year-old dog who loves to play and turns everyday life into extraordinary adventures.

Get the Disney Bundle

From your favorite Disney, Marvel and Star Wars stories on Disney+ to your latest streaming obsessions and Originals on Hulu, to thousands of live sporting events and archives on ESPN+, you're sure to find the streaming bundle that's right for you.

Give the gift of Disney+

Gift a year of endless entertainment.

Disney+ Help Center

Disney+ is the exclusive home for your favorite movies and TV shows from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, and National Geographic.

MARVEL

Marvel.com: The Official Site of Marvel Entertainment

Marvel.com is the official site of Marvel Entertainment! Browse official Marvel movies, characters, comics, TV shows, videos, & more.

Marvel HQ Published by StoryToys

Packed with activities, videos, books comics and more cool stuff featuring characters from the Marvel Universe. Available now on the Apple App Store, on Google Play, or at the Amazon App Store.

The Marvels

When Carol Danvers AKA Captain Marvel’s duties send her to an anomalous wormhole linked to a Kree revolutionary, her powers become entangled with that of Jersey City super-fan Kamala Khan, aka Ms. Marvel, and Carol’s estranged niece, now S.A.B.E.R. astronaut Captain Monica Rambeau.

Dark Phoenix

Follow X-Men's Jean Grey as she evolves into the iconic Dark Phoenix.

Marvel’s Avengers Video Game

Marvel’s Avengers combines an original story with single-player or up to four player co-operative gameplay in the definitive Avengers gaming experience.

Marvel Unlimited – Digital Comic Book Subscription Service

Unlock the Marvel universe, and enjoy instant access to over 25,000 digital comics with Marvel’s premier digital subscription service.

Marvel Movies & the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU)

Explore your favorite Marvel movies and films on the official site of Marvel Entertainment! Discover your favorite plots, characters, cast, & more!

Marvel Characters, Super Heroes, & Villains

Learn about your favorite Marvel characters, super heroes, & villains! Read about Spider-Man, Iron Man, Captain Marvel, Thanos, the Avengers & more!

Marvel TV Shows

Check out all of your favorite Marvel TV shows right here, plus, learn all about the cast, characters and plotlines.

Marvel Games

Explore Marvel's collection of console, online, & mobile games! Check out Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 for PlayStation 5.

Marvel Comics

Explore and purchase Marvel print and digital comics. Marvel.com is the official website to learn about all-things Marvel comics!

WALT DISNEY PICTURES

Wish

In “Wish,” Asha, a sharp-witted idealist, makes a wish so powerful that it is answered by a cosmic force—a little ball of boundless energy called Star.

The Little Mermaid (2023)

The live-action adaptation of Disney's beloved classic "The Little Mermaid" is in theaters now.

Haunted Mansion (2023)

Inspired by the classic theme park attraction, a woman and her son enlist a motley crew of so-called spiritual experts to help rid their home of supernatural squatters.

Disney News

Get the latest news on Disney, Pixar, Disney+, Star Wars, Marvel, and Disney Parks & Resorts here. You can also find the latest from our Disney Magic Moments.

Disney Movie Insiders

Celebrate the movies you love and get rewarded! Earn points for eligible titles, unlock insider perks and redeem points for amazing rewards. Join now!

Movies Anywhere

Enjoy your favorite purchased movies combined into one collection.

Screen Pass

Give someone access to your favorite movie without it ever leaving your collection on Movies Anywhere.

PIXAR

Elemental

The story introduces Ember, a tough, quick-witted and fiery young woman, whose friendship with a fun, sappy, go-with-the-flow guy named Wade challenges her beliefs about the world they live in.

Lightyear

From Disney and Pixar comes an animated sci-fi action-adventure — the definitive origin story of Buzz Lightyear (voice of Chris Evans), the hero who inspired the toy.

STAR WARS

Star Wars News

The most up-to-date source for all Star Wars news.

Star Wars Databank

Learn about Star Wars characters, planets, ships, vehicles, droids, and more in the official Star Wars Databank at StarWars.com.

Star Wars Films

Find information about all Star Wars films.

Star Wars Activities

Discover a galaxy of activities for you and your family.

Star Wars Games

Find information about Star Wars' hottest new games here.

Star Wars Kids

Find games, videos, and activities from Star Wars Kids.

Star Wars Young Jedi Adventures

Watch shorts of your favorite characters from the series Star Wars Young Jedi Adventures.

Star Wars: The High Republic

Original stories from the all new era of the High Republic.

20TH CENTURY STUDIOS

Avatar: The Way of Water

James Cameron returns to the world of Pandora in this emotionally-packed action-adventure set more than a decade after events of the first film.

A Haunting in Venice

Set in eerie, post-World War II Venice on All Hallows’ Eve is a terrifying mystery featuring the return of the celebrated sleuth, Hercule Poirot.

The Boogeyman

When a desperate patient unexpectedly shows up at the home of a therapist and his two daughters, he leaves behind a terrifying supernatural entity that preys on families. A horror-thriller from best-selling author Stephen King.

20th Century Studios

Enjoy all of your favorite movies from 20th Century Studios.

20th Century Studios Family

Family friendly favorites from 20th Century Studios.

ABC NEWS AND ENTERTAINMENT

ABC Breaking News

Get breaking national & world news, broadcast video coverage, and exclusive interviews.

ABC National News

News about United States politics, crime, education, legal stories, celebrities, weather, the economy and more.

538

Prepare for the 2024 election with 538's election polls, politics and analysis.

ABC International News

Get the latest international news and events from Asia, Europe, the Middle East, and more.

ABC News Videos

Get the latest news videos and watch live news clips & coverage online at ABC News.

Official Site of the ABC Network

Visit ABC online for information on ABC daytime and primetime network programming.

Watch Full Episodes from ABC

Watch full episodes from your favorite ABC programs online.

ABC TV Shows

Browse the complete list of our programming as well as movies and specials.

ABC Television Schedule

Official ABC Home Schedule offers a deeper look at the hit TV series.

Grey's Anatomy

The official Grey's Anatomy page on ABC.

ABC Daytime

The View, The Chew, General Hospital, and more.

ESPN

ESPN

Stay updated on all the latest sports news and scores at ESPN.com, the Worldwide Leader in Sports.

SportsCenter

Watch sports video clips, highlights and all the famous SportsCenter commercials at SportsCenter.com.

WatchESPN

Watch live sports events and replays as well as ESPN programs at WatchESPN.com

ESPN+ Stream Live Sports

Watch a selection of live sports from MLB, MLS, NHL, PGA TOUR Golf, Top Rank Boxing, Grand Slam Tennis, college sports, soccer, cricket, rugby and more.

NBA Draft

Get all the latest news around basketball's upcoming NBA draft on ESPN.

Fantasy Football

Play ESPN fantasy football for free. Create or join a fantasy football league, draft players, track rankings, watch highlights, get pick advice, and more!

Andscape
